name: Nifty Royale X Sen3Paul Obsidian Series

metadata.description: After centuries of greed and neglect, we are faced with the threat of eradication. In the race for world domination, our future is in the hands of a sinister creation programmed for destruction.
metadata.name: Obsidian Omega

attributes.value: Sen3Paul is a self-taught, digital 3D artist who is drawn to the subtle intricacies and details of bio mechanical subjects, as well as photo realistic renderings. He is frequently exploring various methods of artistic expression.
